The paper deals with a network information-theoretic approach to study the capacity region of a secure coded caching system. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
